G\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5327156573109657122\" border=\"0\" /></a>But at least another room got painted!</div></p>\n<p>\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Happy Anniversary, Puppy! Can you imagine what we\'ll be doing next year with like a 9-month old? A beach house in Mexico, right...?!!</div></p>\n<p>I love you!!! I raise my glass of Emergen-C to the most special love I have ever known. I cherish every moment together. Still.</p>\n\n<p><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/Se3is1lQ4BI/AAAAAAAAAhA/dNL-1CPd76s/s1600-h/cherry+blossoms+3.JPG\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 150px; height: 113px;\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/Se3is1lQ4BI/AAAAAAAAAhA/dNL-1CPd76s/s320/cherry+blossoms+3.JPG\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5327163194174660626\" border=\"0\" /></a>\n<div class=\"blogger-post-footer\"><img width=\'1\' height=\'1\' src=\'https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/952057894534259836-3809219351364397059?l=building-a-nest.blogspot.com\' /></div>\n</p>',1248120156,1248033756,'',0),('2:72b3da2d8510a90a5d94e2114251cb26','<p>Stella is just over a week old and she has had many visitors since coming home.</p>\n<p>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/Sl-MY8CL9iI/AAAAAAAAAsc/OqrCHesspn0/s1600-h/cimg5220.jpg\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 240px; height: 320px;\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/Sl-MY8CL9iI/AAAAAAAAAsc/OqrCHesspn0/s320/cimg5220.jpg\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5359156441654228514\" border=\"0\" /></a>Nana (Erik\'s mom) meets Stella</div></p>\n\n<p>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_