INSERT INTO `node_revisions` VALUES (13,13,1,'Gallery 2','','','',1248032373,1),(12,12,1,'Gallery 1','beach 1','beach 1','',1248032188,1),(14,14,1,'Building a nest','','','',1248034862,1),(99,99,1,'Baby Shower!','My two sisters and best friend threw me an incredible baby shower.<br /><br /><br /><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibbKEe88SI/AAAAAAAAAlE/iyDILXDoD80/s1600-h/cimg4930.jpg\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 320px; height: 240px;\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibbKEe88SI/AAAAAAAAAlE/iyDILXDoD80/s320/cimg4930.jpg\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5343198973970411810\" border=\"0\" /></a>My oldest sister, Michele, holding the camera (friend Jenna in the long skirt)...<br /></div><br /><br /><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibbKudxQWI/AAAAAAAAAlU/bEbziYdgry4/s1600-h/cimg4917.jpg\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 320px; height: 240px;\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibbKudxQWI/AAAAAAAAAlU/bEbziYdgry4/s320/cimg4917.jpg\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5343198985239740770\" border=\"0\" /></a>My next oldest sister, Lara, working her butt off...<br /></div><br /><br /><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibbKdKsfZI/AAAAAAAAAlM/Tn2m25wGJVU/s1600-h/cimg4936.jpg\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 320px; height: 240px;\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibbKdKsfZI/AAAAAAAAAlM/Tn2m25wGJVU/s320/cimg4936.jpg\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5343198980596333970\" border=\"0\" /></a>And my best friend, Ravyn.<br /></div><br /><br />The spread was really beautiful. There were so many vases of flowers in every room that I kept spotting them even after everyone left!<br /><br /><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibSbFPEPeI/AAAAAAAAAkM/2TVajfG4tAg/s1600-h/cimg4929.jpg\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 320px; height: 240px;\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibSbFPEPeI/AAAAAAAAAkM/2TVajfG4tAg/s320/cimg4929.jpg\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5343189370625342946\" border=\"0\" /></a>They made a beautiful cucumber-mint water, 2 kinds of mimosas and herbal iced tea...<br /></div><br /><br /><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibSaR2EH9I/AAAAAAAAAj8/AIF_WULTlyo/s1600-h/cimg4910.jpg\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 320px; height: 240px;\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibSaR2EH9I/AAAAAAAAAj8/AIF_WULTlyo/s320/cimg4910.jpg\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5343189356830269394\" border=\"0\" /></a>They borrowed huge potted plants to place throughout the house, creating a beautiful garden theme (Francie is enjoying our beach wedding album before the fun gets started).<br /></div><br /><br /><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibSZ3ucsHI/AAAAAAAAAj0/Q6VjMfzNG8A/s1600-h/cimg4908.jpg\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 320px; height: 240px;\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibSZ3ucsHI/AAAAAAAAAj0/Q6VjMfzNG8A/s320/cimg4908.jpg\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5343189349819002994\" border=\"0\" /></a>They made stratas and egg casseroles, beautiful fruit salads and dips, and they had delicious croissants and pastries. In the background is a table set up where everyone painted a birth bead for my labor - I will string them together and carry them around for good luck (or throw them at Erik for knockin\' me up :)<br /></div><br /><br /><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibSZlgjyWI/AAAAAAAAAjs/wde52sYrzH8/s1600-h/cimg4907.jpg\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 320px; height: 240px;\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibSZlgjyWI/AAAAAAAAAjs/wde52sYrzH8/s320/cimg4907.jpg\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5343189344928909666\" border=\"0\" /></a>They framed very sweet pictures of Erik and me  as children (thanks for your help with that, Nancee!). And there were very special photos of me and my mom included. Behind the photos on the right is a meaningful gardenia plant, my mother\'s very favorite plant and scent. A huge effort was made to have her all around me as we celebrated. We even ate on her china. It was so painful not having her there, but she felt so close with all of these things reminding me of her. I know she would have really loved it.<br /></div><br /><br /><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibYS959_OI/AAAAAAAAAk8/mWlXId4PpBU/s1600-h/cimg4932.jpg\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 320px; height: 240px;\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibYS959_OI/AAAAAAAAAk8/mWlXId4PpBU/s320/cimg4932.jpg\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5343195828288617698\" border=\"0\" /></a>We gathered to eat all the delicious food...<br /></div><br /><br /><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibSa6m1ixI/AAAAAAAAAkE/6PhzueFZud8/s1600-h/cimg4914.jpg\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 320px; height: 240px;\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibSa6m1ixI/AAAAAAAAAkE/6PhzueFZud8/s320/cimg4914.jpg\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5343189367772252946\" border=\"0\" /></a>And then we had delicious (and beautiful) cake while we played funny games and opened presents!<br /></div><br /><br /><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibWk_DICVI/AAAAAAAAAkc/q3QknMRNvjg/s1600-h/cimg4979.jpg\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 320px; height: 240px;\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibWk_DICVI/AAAAAAAAAkc/q3QknMRNvjg/s320/cimg4979.jpg\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5343193938809850194\" border=\"0\" /></a>One of my favorites... Can you believe how perfect?!<br /></div><br /><br /><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibWlpml_2I/AAAAAAAAAks/1AuF-K-Xsa0/s1600-h/cimg4950.jpg\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 320px; height: 240px;\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibWlpml_2I/AAAAAAAAAks/1AuF-K-Xsa0/s320/cimg4950.jpg\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5343193950232903522\" border=\"0\" /></a>I had lots of help from my nieces (they even took these photos of present-opening)...<br /><br /><br /><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibWlBUx7II/AAAAAAAAAkk/o46oMCExHww/s1600-h/cimg4953.jpg\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 320px; height: 240px;\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibWlBUx7II/AAAAAAAAAkk/o46oMCExHww/s320/cimg4953.jpg\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5343193939420769410\" border=\"0\" /></a>And they decorated my head.<br /></div><br /><br /><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibWk6pMiGI/AAAAAAAAAkU/rqKnKATSQOs/s1600-h/cimg4939.jpg\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 320px; height: 240px;\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SibWk6pMiGI/AAAAAAAAAkU/rqKnKATSQOs/s320/cimg4939.jpg\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5343193937627351138\" border=\"0\" /></a>Thank you Ravyn for recording who gave us what and for clearing the trash as I tore through all the great presents!<br /><br /><br /><div style=\"text-align: left;\">And thank you to my beautiful sisters and friend who threw me such an amazing shower. It was a really beautiful welcoming for Firecracker, so beautiful it looked like a wedding. I am so touched by all of the effort and time that went into planning and throwing this event. I will never forget that day and how special and loved I felt. Love and support are such great things to be feeling right before I do one of the hardest and most amazing things I\'ve ever done: give birth to my child (at home). I really feel the love and support surrounding me and I can\'t think of anything better to prepare me for this experience.<br /><br />Thank you and I love you all!<br /></div></div><div class=\"blogger-post-footer\"><img width=\'1\' height=\'1\' src=\'https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/952057894534259836-4657534894014786027?l=building-a-nest.blogspot.com\'/></div>','My two sisters and best friend threw me an incredible baby shower.<br /><br />','',1248034898,2),(100,100,1,'California and Other Updates','We had a lovely visit to California for Erik\'s grandpa\'s surprise 80th birthday party. Lucky us, a baby shower was thrown for us as a cover for the surprise b-day party!<br /><br /><br /><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SgNWEE-bV6I/AAAAAAAAAjY/j72KYVX0ACY/s1600-h/CIMG4724.JPG\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 320px; height: 240px;\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SgNWEE-bV6I/AAAAAAAAAjY/j72KYVX0ACY/s320/CIMG4724.JPG\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5333201011791845282\" border=\"0\" /></a>Beautiful quilt handmade by Erik\'s Aunt Shirley!<br /></div><br /><br /><br /><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SgNWV-_TSGI/AAAAAAAAAjg/L9YpjthjxIg/s1600-h/CIMG4731.JPG\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 320px; height: 240px;\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SgNWV-_TSGI/AAAAAAAAAjg/L9YpjthjxIg/s320/CIMG4731.JPG\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5333201319422543970\" border=\"0\" /></a>Sweet presents from Erik\'s Grandma & Grandpa Whalen<br /></div><br /><br /><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SgNWDrMDSOI/AAAAAAAAAjQ/BPvNbdbdp38/s1600-h/CIMG4712.JPG\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 320px; height: 240px;\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SgNWDrMDSOI/AAAAAAAAAjQ/BPvNbdbdp38/s320/CIMG4712.JPG\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5333201004869667042\" border=\"0\" /></a>And from the secret agent cousin in the background (don\'t listen to her, Firecracker - you\'re not to be a future agent...).<br /></div><br /><br /><br /><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SgNWDVG6FjI/AAAAAAAAAjI/ixvMRfXQ4Xo/s1600-h/CIMG4702.JPG\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 320px; height: 240px;\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SgNWDVG6FjI/AAAAAAAAAjI/ixvMRfXQ4Xo/s320/CIMG4702.JPG\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5333200998942512690\" border=\"0\" /></a>Erik\'s grandpa (in the patterned shirt) - lookin\' good at 80!! Boy was he surprised when 50 of his family and friends showed up after the baby shower!<br /></div><br /><br /><br /><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SgNWC71M84I/AAAAAAAAAjA/qStuvTY_PPA/s1600-h/CIMG4777.JPG\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 320px; height: 240px;\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SgNWC71M84I/AAAAAAAAAjA/qStuvTY_PPA/s320/CIMG4777.JPG\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5333200992157365122\" border=\"0\" /></a>And we had a lovely day at the beach the day before we left.<br /><br /></div><br /><br /><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SgNWChdadUI/AAAAAAAAAi4/PQ5aM6QiN1c/s1600-h/CIMG4772.JPG\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 320px; height: 240px;\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SgNWChdadUI/AAAAAAAAAi4/PQ5aM6QiN1c/s320/CIMG4772.JPG\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5333200985078265154\" border=\"0\" /></a>Fed Firecracker a yummy sandwich on the beach.<br /><br /><br /></div><br /><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_XJiKR9ud4U0/SgNUvaF_W8I/AAAAAAAAAio/Nyij0gBLuEU/s1